cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in research, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "supercut-judge-cascade"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2024-01-01"
abstract: >
  Vision-LLM 3-stage judge cascade with ArcFace identity gating for video
  supercut generation. Combines a cheap defect gate (Stage C), a mid-tier
  viewer-perspective scorer (Stage A), and an expensive editor-perspective
  scorer (Stage B) via litellm for provider-agnostic model access.
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/example/supercut-judge-cascade"
keywords:
  - video
  - supercut
  - vision-llm
  - face-recognition
  - arcface
  - judge-cascade
  - scene-detection
